verbose_text: In this pathway, an alpha-secretase cleaves APP within the Abeta peptide sequence, which precludes the formation of neurotoxic Abeta peptides, and produces sAPPalpha, a neurotrophic and neuroprotective fragment [XREF_BIBR].
